OL,3,CGrief group using sewing to help cope
OL,4,Cwith bereavement
OL,6,Freports from the bereavement cafe in
OL,7,FBolton where a sewing project is
OL,8,Fhelping people cope with their grief.
OL,10,FA group set up to offer help to those
OL,11,Fstruggling with grief is producing a
OL,12,Fspecial memorial quilt, which is hoped
OL,13,Fwill start a much-needed conversation
OL,14,Fabout bereavement.
OL,16,FThe Bereavement Cafe in is a charity
OL,17,Fthat was set up in 2021, offering peer-
OL,18,Fto-peer support for those struggling
OL,19,Fwith the loss of a loved one.
