OL,6,FThe group has now been given funding
OL,7,Fto make a quilt which will be
OL,8,Fdisplayed across the country.
OL,10,F"I do hope when it is displayed it
OL,11,Fwill help people have those
OL,12,Fconversations or make them think about
OL,13,Fpeople around them who maybe are
OL,14,Fgrieving," says Jane Dixon who set up
OL,15,Fthe charity.
OL,17,F"They may have thought, she's back at
OL,18,Fwork she's probably doing ok. I want
OL,19,Fthem to think, actually they're
OL,20,Fprobably not OK, shall I check in on
OL,21,Fthem."
