OL,6,F"People were telling me, you need
OL,7,Fcounselling, but I didn't personally
OL,8,Ffeel that I needed counselling, I just
OL,9,Fneeded to talk to somebody who knew
OL,10,Fwhat I was going through, but there
OL,11,Fwas nothing like that around."
OL,13,FThat is what prompted Jane to set up
OL,14,Fthe charity.
OL,16,FThe cafes move around different venues
OL,17,Fevery week across Bolton and Wigan and
OL,18,Foffer a safe, informal place to
OL,19,Fprovide peer-to-peer support for those
OL,20,Fstruggling with grief.
