OL,6,FThe sewing group is an off-shoot of
OL,7,Fthe cafe meetings are are open to
OL,8,Fanyone, male or female, and they're
OL,9,Fkeen to encourage more people to join
OL,10,Fin.
OL,12,FSusan Phelan joined the group about a
OL,13,Fyear ago after losing her daughter
OL,14,FLaura suddenly.
OL,16,F"I just turned up one particular day
OL,17,Fand it has just been a lifeline for
OL,18,Fme," she told ITV's Granada Reports.
OL,20,F"I can't talk to my family the same as
OL,21,FI can talk to people here."
