OL,4,Cwith bereavement
OL,6,FSharon and her son have both been
OL,7,Fhelped by the Bereavement Cafe after
OL,8,Fshe lost her husband Chris.
OL,10,F"It has enabled me to talk about my
OL,11,Ffeelings, about the grief - it is that
OL,12,Fsafe space where you can cry.
OL,14,F"We laugh as well, we don't just sit
OL,15,Faround and be gloomy, and I can just
OL,16,Ftalk to people who know what you're
OL,17,Fgoing through."
